  "title": "Interior Sales Designer (Junior / Senior Roles)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>· Industry/ Organization: Manufacturer (Carpentry, Interior Design & Renovation)</p><p>· Position Title: Sales Interior Designer</p><p><br /></p><p>Role & Responsibilities:</p><p>• Handle sales enquiry and provide quotation</p><p>• Measuring customer site, determining the cost of completion and project requirements.</p><p>• Advise and prepare space planning, quotations and schedule to present to customers</p><p>• Liaise with customers to understand their renovation preferences and requirements.</p><p>• Conceptualize and sketch design plans.</p><p>• Present 3D perspective drawings to client, and pitch the complete design decisions</p><p>• Liaise with designers concerning interior design layouts and drawings standards/details. Identifying and communicating potential problems to the team.</p><p>• Work with different stakeholders (ie. customers and contractors/vendors) to coordinate the renovation work.</p><p>• Oversee and set a timeline to ensure of smooth completion of the project.</p><p>• Conduct on-site inspection to ensure quality workmanship are achieved</p><p>•Manage project renovation sites</p><p>• Any ad hoc duties as assigned.</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• Possess good presentation, communication & interpersonal skills</p><p>• Able to communicate with mandarin speaking subcons</p><p>• Ability to manage multiple projects and timelines</p><p>• Independent and able to multi-tasked.</p><p>• Good team player</p><p>• Strong ownership and proactive in learning</p><p>• Proficient in Illustration, AutoCAD or sketchup</p><p>• At least 2 years of relevant local Singapore experience.<br /><br />• Preferable to speak Mandarin.</p><p>Kindly apply through ANY of the following methods:</p><p>· Submit your application by clicking the APPLY button;</p><p>· Email your resume to yukipeck.lexx@gmail.com</p><p>· We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
